messages.message:
Hi all, if you could quickly vote on :point_up: , that would be great. What we are asking is related to release notes.
Currently we have
 Infrastructure, Bug Fixes, and App

We want to move things to:
Infrastructure, Platform, App, Bug Fixes

The difference between Platform and Infrastructure will be: Platform == ACL, Launcher, etc. Infrastructure will be things like performance enhancements, changes to redis, etc
